      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td><code>crit</code> </td>

        <td>致命的な状態</td>
       <td>socket: Failed to get a socket, exiting child
       (socket: ソケットが得世蕕譴覆い燭瓠∋劵廛蹈札垢鮟擦気擦箴
